        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[[吃惊]#卵巢早衰# 每天一大早都能随机吓死一个90后[泪]，该说还得说，科普来一波！以下症状可能是卵巢发出的“求救信号”，咱还是别大意👇🏻[星星]经期不规...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[吃惊]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chijing-59b444adb6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%8D%B5%E5%B7%A2%E6%97%A9%E8%A1%B0%23&amp;isnewpage=1" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#卵巢早衰#</span></a> 每天一大早都能随机吓死一个90后<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[泪]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_lei-4cdf6ee412.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>，该说还得说，科普来一波！以下症状可能是卵巢发出的“求救信号”，咱还是别大意👇🏻<br><br><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[星星]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/_/x_star1-e5d754c7b6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>经期不规律：这是卵巢早衰的重要信号；<br><br><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[星星]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/_/x_star1-e5d754c7b6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>内分泌异常：白带出现异味、异色，阴道分泌物过少；<br><br><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[星星]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/_/x_star1-e5d754c7b6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>情绪不稳：烦躁、易怒、工作效率降低；<br><br><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[星星]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/_/x_star1-e5d754c7b6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>皮肤：肤色略显暗淡、无弹性、出现皱纹和色斑等；<br><br><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[星星]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/_/x_star1-e5d754c7b6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>睡眠：失眠多梦、入睡困难，夜间睡觉大量出汗；<br><br><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[星星]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/_/x_star1-e5d754c7b6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>发胖：小腹臃肿、水桶腰、臀部下垂；<br><br><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[星星]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/_/x_star1-e5d754c7b6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>骨关节：经常出现不明原因的关节疼痛、腰酸背痛，易出现骨折；<br><br><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[星星]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/_/x_star1-e5d754c7b6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>性生活障碍：性冷淡、性交痛等。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（深圳市人民医院）<img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hkip6ddobjj20m8093q3d.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
            <pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 02:22:35 GMT</pubDate>
