            <title><![CDATA[#接吻会不会传染幽门螺杆菌#[二哈]不会！（只要对象不介意[偷乐]幽门螺旋杆菌传播途径尚不明确，目前认为，主要传播方式是粪口相传、口口相传。小朋友感染风险较...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%8E%A5%E5%90%BB%E4%BC%9A%E4%B8%8D%E4%BC%9A%E4%BC%A0%E6%9F%93%E5%B9%BD%E9%97%A8%E8%9E%BA%E6%9D%86%E8%8F%8C%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%8E%A5%E5%90%BB%E4%BC%9A%E4%B8%8D%E4%BC%9A%E4%BC%A0%E6%9F%93%E5%B9%BD%E9%97%A8%E8%9E%BA%E6%9D%86%E8%8F%8C%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#接吻会不会传染幽门螺杆菌#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[二哈]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_erha-139d0e07bd.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><br><br>不会！（只要对象不介意<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[偷乐]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/lxh/lxh_toule-244c58c525.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><br><br>幽门螺旋杆菌传播途径尚不明确，目前认为，主要传播方式是粪口相传、口口相传。小朋友感染风险较高，成年人对活菌有一定免疫能力。幽门螺旋杆菌主要在胃里，口腔中含量较低，接吻感染几率也较低。但是！如果接吻频繁、共餐频繁等，还是有一定几率会交叉感染哦！<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫来辟谣#</span></a>（深圳市人民医院）<img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hkht5n66qsj20u00watb4.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
